WEBVTT

02:24.480 --> 02:26.880
The only way to destroy Jiu Ying

02:26.960 --> 02:29.360
is for each of us to devour
one of its heads,

02:29.440 --> 02:31.280
then transform into mountain ranges

02:31.360 --> 02:32.920
to seal it beneath us.

02:33.000 --> 02:33.880
Chi Wen,

02:34.400 --> 02:36.160
you carry the power of sealing.

02:36.240 --> 02:37.440
The final burden

02:37.960 --> 02:39.200
falls on you.

02:39.280 --> 02:41.440
But who will seal you?

02:41.520 --> 02:44.040
What if Jiu Ying takes over your body?

02:44.120 --> 02:45.920
Don't worry, my brothers.

02:46.000 --> 02:48.800
I'll drive the Guili Sword
into my dragon's spine

02:48.880 --> 02:50.240
to pin down Jiu Ying's primordial spirit.

02:50.320 --> 02:53.120
Then, I'll return to Shilin Sect,
find a suitable vessel,

02:53.960 --> 02:57.200
and transfer the spirit into it
using the Dragonbirth Spell,

02:57.280 --> 02:58.800
to seal away my true dragon form.

02:59.640 --> 03:00.640
After that,

03:02.040 --> 03:04.920
I'll be the one
to keep the world at peace.

03:32.920 --> 03:35.040
I'm afraid a suitable vessel

03:35.120 --> 03:36.640
won't be easy to find.

03:40.200 --> 03:42.840
You're back. How was it, Chi Wen?

03:46.040 --> 03:47.000
In that case,

03:47.640 --> 03:49.440
there's only one last way.

03:50.920 --> 03:53.760
We fuse our reverse scales

03:53.840 --> 03:55.760
and create a Tenth Dragon.

03:56.280 --> 03:59.360
He will become
a final hope for this world.

04:33.680 --> 04:34.680
That is me.

04:37.680 --> 04:38.760
The Tenth Dragon.

04:57.560 --> 04:59.000
Why isn't he back yet?

05:38.880 --> 05:40.200
He's fine.

05:40.720 --> 05:42.720
Take them back to Shilin Sect.

05:43.560 --> 05:45.520
Yes. Master Dragon Deity,

05:46.120 --> 05:47.240
Wu Zhiqi

05:48.080 --> 05:49.120
has a request.

05:50.240 --> 05:51.160
I know.

05:51.680 --> 05:55.040
He has mentioned it to me before.

05:57.320 --> 05:58.480
You all go ahead.

06:24.760 --> 06:26.040
Should I stay?

06:32.920 --> 06:33.960
Accompany me somewhere.

08:10.880 --> 08:12.320
Your hands are dirty.

08:13.080 --> 08:16.000
Can you really leave it unwashed?

08:24.720 --> 08:27.200
Last time I refused to wash my hands,

08:27.280 --> 08:28.560
Master Dragon Deity,

08:29.080 --> 08:31.920
you shoved my hands
into the water brutally.

08:32.720 --> 08:34.360
This isn't an illusion.

08:35.360 --> 08:36.600
And I'm not Man Man.

08:39.280 --> 08:40.919
Don't test the Dragon Deity's patience.

08:43.520 --> 08:44.680
Right.

08:46.440 --> 08:48.680
You're no longer a dragon
on the chopping block.

08:49.200 --> 08:50.040
What a shame.

08:52.680 --> 08:53.920
But what if

08:54.720 --> 08:56.440
I insist?

09:25.280 --> 09:26.400
<i>If so,</i>

09:26.480 --> 09:28.640
<i>I'll take the ring.</i>

09:29.240 --> 09:30.720
It's been hundreds of years,

09:31.400 --> 09:34.840
and you still act like a reckless child.

09:35.560 --> 09:37.000
If you want to try,

09:37.960 --> 09:39.200
go ahead then.

10:02.320 --> 10:04.760
You washed my hands twice before.

10:05.480 --> 10:06.560
I remember.

10:19.440 --> 10:22.960
The scent on you has faded.

10:35.400 --> 10:36.480
This handkerchief…

10:37.600 --> 10:38.600
Why do you still keep it?

13:17.520 --> 13:19.160
Where's Master Dragon Deity?

13:19.800 --> 13:22.200
Don't worry, Commander Li. He is safe.

13:22.280 --> 13:24.360
The butterfly demon has been subdued.

13:24.880 --> 13:26.880
Dragon Deity's Power
on Wu Zhiqi has been reclaimed.

13:28.320 --> 13:30.320
But your body…

13:31.200 --> 13:32.240
I'm fine.

13:33.280 --> 13:34.240
Bai Ze,

13:34.920 --> 13:36.000
who exactly

13:37.080 --> 13:38.640
is Yuan Wuhuo?

13:39.240 --> 13:40.600
Master Dragon Deity,

13:40.680 --> 13:42.720
are you still thinking
about the butterfly demon?

13:43.680 --> 13:44.760
Who is he?

13:46.600 --> 13:47.720
To me,

13:50.000 --> 13:50.960
he

13:54.360 --> 13:56.240
was once like a brother.

13:59.080 --> 13:59.960
Was he a dragon too?

14:02.320 --> 14:03.160
No.

14:05.080 --> 14:06.160
He was a human.

14:07.560 --> 14:09.920
Once the demon hunter commander
of the Shilin Sect.

14:11.400 --> 14:12.600
He watched me grow up,

14:13.800 --> 14:15.280
and I stayed with him
until the end of his life.

14:53.720 --> 14:55.120
<i>When I first met him,</i>

14:55.640 --> 14:56.880
<i>he was a proud man.</i>

14:57.400 --> 14:59.000
<i>A great hero.</i>

15:01.040 --> 15:03.120
<i>And when I saw him off</i>
<i>on his final journey,</i>

15:03.200 --> 15:06.040
<i>he was an old man worn down by illness.</i>

15:07.800 --> 15:08.840
<i>A mortal lifespan</i>

15:09.760 --> 15:11.800
<i>is the greatest shackle in this world.</i>

15:13.520 --> 15:15.000
Since he was a human,

15:16.800 --> 15:18.840
how did he become a butterfly demon?

15:22.120 --> 15:23.200
And why

15:26.480 --> 15:28.280
does he look exactly like me?

15:30.680 --> 15:31.960
I understand now.

15:32.800 --> 15:34.440
Like Wangyan and I.

15:34.520 --> 15:36.680
Although we're not related by blood,

15:37.200 --> 15:39.280
we hold each other dear.

15:40.360 --> 15:43.160
Even knowing she's hiding
something from me,

15:44.840 --> 15:46.720
I still refuse to believe it.

15:48.440 --> 15:49.840
I don't want to lose her.

15:50.560 --> 15:51.880
You won't lose her.

15:52.400 --> 15:55.280
Can you tell me what secret
you're keeping with her?

15:56.480 --> 15:57.400
Tell me,

15:57.920 --> 15:59.400
and I won't lose her.

16:01.120 --> 16:02.360
I can help you too.

16:36.800 --> 16:38.280
<i>This is the Moon Summoning Pearl.</i>

16:39.320 --> 16:41.880
<i>Hold it, and channel your power.</i>

16:43.200 --> 16:44.720
No matter where I am,

16:45.440 --> 16:47.520
I'll come to you at once.

16:48.880 --> 16:49.920
Wu Wangyan.

16:52.760 --> 16:54.040
Come to me.

17:25.839 --> 17:27.000
Be careful.

17:27.079 --> 17:28.119
I can see.

17:51.600 --> 17:54.240
Shouldn't you return
the Moon Summoning Pearl?

17:57.920 --> 17:59.040
Aren't you going to ask

18:00.520 --> 18:01.800
why I summoned you here?

18:02.760 --> 18:04.000
If you want to tell me,

18:04.520 --> 18:05.720
you will.

18:06.840 --> 18:09.280
If not, there's no point asking.

18:26.000 --> 18:27.640
If I hadn't used it to summon you,

18:28.360 --> 18:30.160
would you have kept avoiding me?

18:31.840 --> 18:33.160
I was just tired

18:34.960 --> 18:36.600
and wanted peace

18:37.720 --> 18:39.240
somewhere quiet.

18:40.280 --> 18:41.600
What happened in the illusion…

18:45.440 --> 18:46.440
Go ahead and ask.

18:48.600 --> 18:51.960
I'll tell you everything you want to know.

18:54.600 --> 18:55.880
Let's treat this

18:58.160 --> 18:59.000
as a final farewell.

19:10.200 --> 19:13.320
You should know, on every full moon night,

19:13.400 --> 19:15.320
all members of the Formless Moon Sect

19:15.400 --> 19:17.120
are forcibly summoned back
to the Formless Moon Palace

19:17.200 --> 19:18.840
by the Power of the Moon.

19:29.160 --> 19:30.800
<i>Once we enter the Sacred Spring,</i>

19:31.720 --> 19:35.080
<i>there are no secrets between us.</i>

19:36.520 --> 19:38.040
<i>Each rebirth</i>

19:38.560 --> 19:40.360
<i>reshapes the body</i>

19:40.440 --> 19:42.480
<i>and restores memory and emotion.</i>

19:43.000 --> 19:44.400
One day,

19:45.680 --> 19:47.480
the Oracle Stone delivered a prophecy.

19:48.680 --> 19:49.680
We were to wipe out

19:49.760 --> 19:51.240
a village by the Blackwater River
where flood dragons dwelled.

19:52.440 --> 19:55.400
I objected. We argued.

19:56.040 --> 19:57.040
Master,

19:58.160 --> 20:01.720
if there are sinners among them,
punishing those responsible is enough.

20:01.800 --> 20:03.760
Why must we destroy the entire clan?

20:04.680 --> 20:08.080
The world has its balance.

20:09.000 --> 20:10.600
The Oracle Stone is never wrong.

20:11.520 --> 20:13.520
Their time is up.

20:13.600 --> 20:15.200
No one can defy fate.

20:17.680 --> 20:19.640
<i>It was cruel to exterminate</i>
<i>an entire clan.</i>

20:19.720 --> 20:21.640
We all had doubts

20:22.240 --> 20:23.320
and hesitated.

20:23.840 --> 20:25.240
We didn't act immediately.

20:25.320 --> 20:27.440
But when we woke again,

20:28.440 --> 20:29.600
my memory

20:30.200 --> 20:33.280
had reset to the last time
I entered the Sacred Spring.

20:33.360 --> 20:35.720
It happened to everyone.

20:36.840 --> 20:39.760
We had been reborn.

21:05.640 --> 21:07.320
Master,

21:07.400 --> 21:09.400
thank you for granting us new life.

21:12.160 --> 21:14.240
<i>Xie Lingxi killed you.</i>

21:17.200 --> 21:18.480
<i>But he didn't know</i>

21:20.080 --> 21:21.400
<i>the Power of the Moon</i>

21:22.640 --> 21:24.320
<i>grants us eternal life.</i>

21:29.520 --> 21:31.640
<i>The Fox Queen never mentioned</i>
<i>that mission again.</i>

21:32.160 --> 21:33.960
<i>As if it had never happened.</i>

21:35.560 --> 21:37.560
<i>Even the memory</i>
<i>of our argument and the mission</i>

21:37.640 --> 21:39.880
<i>was never stored</i>
<i>in the Primordial Sacred Spring.</i>

21:40.400 --> 21:41.760
<i>No one remembered.</i>

21:44.960 --> 21:47.080
<i>I went back alone to the Blackwater River.</i>

21:48.560 --> 21:50.280
<i>No one survived.</i>

21:52.000 --> 21:55.280
<i>But traces of my power were everywhere.</i>

21:59.720 --> 22:00.560
<i>That was</i>

22:01.360 --> 22:03.800
when I realized I had committed slaughter.

22:05.120 --> 22:08.120
But I didn't know
they were the flood dragons.

22:09.000 --> 22:10.920
Only after entering the Star Stone

22:11.720 --> 22:13.600
did my memories slowly return.

22:15.080 --> 22:17.000
That was when

22:18.400 --> 22:19.760
I understood

22:20.720 --> 22:23.200
that the Fox Queen's consciousness
had never awakened.

22:23.800 --> 22:26.200
The one controlling us
through the Oracle Stone

22:27.360 --> 22:29.160
-was actually…
-It was Jiu Ying.

22:31.000 --> 22:31.960
Yes.

22:33.920 --> 22:35.920
Jiu Ying used the Oracle Stone

22:36.000 --> 22:37.440
to control the Formless Moon Sect.

22:39.640 --> 22:41.440
I was under his control too.

22:41.960 --> 22:43.080
I had no choice.

22:43.680 --> 22:45.600
Even now, you're still lying to me.

22:46.880 --> 22:49.440
You said you lost
your memories after rebirth.

22:50.040 --> 22:51.480
Then how do you remember all this?

22:52.240 --> 22:54.040
If Jiu Ying erased your memories,

22:54.120 --> 22:56.480
he wouldn't leave any clues
for you to discover.

23:10.320 --> 23:12.240
Your brother helped me.

23:14.400 --> 23:15.360
My brother?

23:15.960 --> 23:20.160
Your brother, the Ninth Dragon, Chi Wen.

23:20.880 --> 23:22.400
Master Chi Wen left you a message.

23:22.480 --> 23:24.560
The Oracle Stone can't be trusted.

23:24.640 --> 23:25.840
If you have doubts,

23:26.840 --> 23:29.480
seal part of your memories
inside this artifact.

23:30.280 --> 23:33.400
Retrieve them later,
and they'll remind you of the truth.

23:34.960 --> 23:37.000
Among all the sisters
in the Formless Moon Sect,

23:37.520 --> 23:40.200
I'm the only one
who still remembers the massacre.

23:40.800 --> 23:43.440
Perhaps because I doubted and resisted,

23:44.320 --> 23:45.960
Jiu Ying chose me as his vessel.

23:47.480 --> 23:48.360
After that,

23:48.880 --> 23:50.800
I didn't dare let him sense
anything unusual.

23:51.440 --> 23:53.360
Before entering the Sacred Spring,

23:54.080 --> 23:56.440
I would always seal away
any memories or emotions

23:56.520 --> 23:57.720
that might expose me.

24:01.280 --> 24:03.400
Any memories or emotions
that might expose you?

24:10.200 --> 24:11.200
Does that include me?

24:25.640 --> 24:26.760
I suppose

24:27.720 --> 24:29.400
that answer

24:30.520 --> 24:31.800
doesn't matter to you anymore.

24:37.680 --> 24:40.680
So you never intended
to carry out the dragon-slaying plan.

24:41.720 --> 24:43.400
Saying you'd slay the dragon with me

24:44.160 --> 24:45.280
was a lie.

24:46.680 --> 24:49.320
You and Chi Wen planned all this together.

24:50.840 --> 24:51.680
Right?

24:51.760 --> 24:53.080
That's right.

24:54.720 --> 24:56.120
He told me to stay close to you

24:57.000 --> 24:58.880
and find a way to get
the prayer bead bracelet.

24:59.440 --> 25:00.840
You and Chi Wen

25:01.440 --> 25:03.960
share the same dragon lineage,
yet you're strangers to each other.

25:04.920 --> 25:08.000
Fate has been cruel.

25:12.080 --> 25:14.000
So you stayed by my side

25:14.520 --> 25:15.880
for the prayer bead bracelet.

25:17.600 --> 25:18.600
I thought…

25:20.280 --> 25:21.280
I thought…

25:31.760 --> 25:33.560
The Twelve thoughts
weren't found in the illusion.

25:33.640 --> 25:35.480
You couldn't succeed.

25:40.120 --> 25:42.080
But I gained something there too.

25:44.440 --> 25:46.120
Something I never expected.

25:48.840 --> 25:49.960
And just as quickly,

25:50.840 --> 25:52.440
I lost it.

25:55.440 --> 25:57.200
Hasn't the boy returned yet?

25:57.720 --> 25:59.760
He went for training with his master.

25:59.840 --> 26:00.920
He'll be back tomorrow.

26:01.880 --> 26:03.080
Here.

26:03.160 --> 26:05.320
Try the water. Is it too hot? Here.

26:12.200 --> 26:13.240
Is it too hot?

26:17.720 --> 26:20.280
You shouldn't stay cooped up all day.

26:20.360 --> 26:21.720
Your legs are getting weak.

26:22.920 --> 26:24.240
I'll take you out for a walk.

26:24.320 --> 26:25.880
Go do your work.

26:25.960 --> 26:27.040
Don't worry about me.

26:27.920 --> 26:29.400
In this illusion,

26:29.480 --> 26:30.920
you're the only one who's real.

26:31.440 --> 26:32.640
Everything else is fake.

26:32.720 --> 26:35.920
-So what's the point of dealing with them?
-I'm not real either.

26:40.040 --> 26:41.200
Or do you really think

26:42.680 --> 26:44.680
I'm your wife?

26:52.600 --> 26:54.640
Time can be erased.

26:54.720 --> 26:56.120
Memories too.

26:56.200 --> 26:58.320
Would you do that?

27:00.320 --> 27:01.720
Would you forget

27:03.200 --> 27:04.560
the truth you've just learned

27:05.240 --> 27:07.840
and return to the peaceful life
we once had?

27:10.640 --> 27:12.960
That peaceful life over those past decades

27:13.840 --> 27:15.160
belongs to my parents.

27:16.120 --> 27:17.040
Not to you.

27:19.120 --> 27:20.440
And not to us.

27:40.040 --> 27:42.200
You can't let go of the hatred,

27:43.080 --> 27:45.120
and I can't wash the blood from my hands.

27:47.680 --> 27:48.520
So,

27:50.120 --> 27:51.120
let me go.

27:54.240 --> 27:55.880
Let yourself go too.

27:56.400 --> 27:59.080
Let him go. And let us be free, alright?

28:15.680 --> 28:17.040
Is Wu Shiguang

28:21.120 --> 28:22.880
really the Tenth Dragon?

28:26.840 --> 28:28.320
And Master Dragon Deity…

28:29.280 --> 28:32.320
Everything happens as it should.
The ending is written in the star.

28:33.160 --> 28:36.200
We know that, don't we?

28:44.840 --> 28:45.920
I should get going.

28:48.480 --> 28:49.920
It's the full moon tonight.

28:50.520 --> 28:51.960
I have to return.

29:13.680 --> 29:15.560
Going home should be a good thing.

29:16.960 --> 29:18.160
Why do you look sad?

29:22.920 --> 29:26.640
Once I return to the Formless Moon Sect
and enter the Primordial Sacred Spring,

29:28.120 --> 29:31.880
everything you and Wangyan planned
will be exposed to the Fox Queen.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.880
If you don't share your memory…

29:36.760 --> 29:38.280
will you tell her?

29:42.400 --> 29:43.480
I don't know.

29:45.840 --> 29:48.000
I don't want to betray
the Formless Moon Sect.

29:52.840 --> 29:54.240
But I understand

29:55.000 --> 29:56.560
why Wangyan wanted to leave.

29:58.440 --> 29:59.920
When you've been bound for too long,

30:02.760 --> 30:04.200
you start wanting to break free.

30:06.200 --> 30:08.920
Everyone's the same.

30:10.000 --> 30:11.960
You can change your face,
reshape your body,

30:12.040 --> 30:13.760
but the heart is the hardest thing
to disguise.

30:15.120 --> 30:16.400
When you long for something

30:18.240 --> 30:19.720
but can't go after it,

30:22.680 --> 30:24.200
that's the saddest thing of all.

30:26.600 --> 30:29.600
Just like when you killed that child.

30:30.480 --> 30:32.080
You knew it had to be done,

30:33.520 --> 30:37.320
but seeing your hands covered in blood

30:38.680 --> 30:40.280
still hurts,

30:41.600 --> 30:42.440
doesn't it?

30:48.000 --> 30:49.200
Why are you crying?

30:53.080 --> 30:54.120
You knew.

30:56.600 --> 30:58.040
You knew everything.

30:58.560 --> 31:01.120
You knew I hate getting my hands dirty.

31:01.200 --> 31:03.400
You knew I liked everlasting flowers.

31:06.280 --> 31:08.000
You even knew I'm Hui.

31:12.360 --> 31:13.480
But those things,

31:16.640 --> 31:18.400
only Ji Ling knew.

31:18.480 --> 31:19.480
Next time we meet,

31:19.560 --> 31:21.040
I'll make you a flower

31:21.120 --> 31:23.240
that will never wither.
Would you like that?

31:23.320 --> 31:24.760
<i>My love for Di Zhu</i>

31:24.840 --> 31:27.200
<i>is like that beautiful everlasting flower.</i>

31:27.760 --> 31:29.000
<i>It will never fade.</i>

31:29.960 --> 31:31.520
Because my moon phase

31:32.440 --> 31:33.280
is Hui.

31:33.360 --> 31:37.360
When you can't see the moon at night,
that moon phase

31:37.960 --> 31:39.000
is Hui.

31:39.080 --> 31:41.080
The sky is pitch black.

31:41.160 --> 31:42.000
There's no moon.

31:42.880 --> 31:43.800
There is.

31:45.160 --> 31:46.200
It's called Hui.

31:47.280 --> 31:49.280
Did you devour Ji Ling

31:51.520 --> 31:53.120
and inherit his memory?

31:57.920 --> 31:59.160
Or

32:04.120 --> 32:05.480
are you Ji Ling?

32:11.800 --> 32:13.320
If it's the former,

32:16.840 --> 32:17.800
what would you do?

32:20.600 --> 32:21.880
I'd hate you.

32:28.280 --> 32:30.000
I'd hate myself too.

32:39.680 --> 32:40.800
Then,

32:41.920 --> 32:43.240
if it's the latter?

32:47.040 --> 32:47.880
Then I…

34:13.800 --> 34:15.400
Perhaps before long,

34:17.280 --> 34:19.280
you'll end up like me.

34:22.080 --> 34:23.159
Don't become like me.

34:25.120 --> 34:26.159
It's not worth it.

34:40.880 --> 34:43.040
It's been so long
since I last saw his face.

34:43.760 --> 34:46.560
Lately, I keep thinking
about when he was a kid.

34:48.800 --> 34:51.159
The first time he called me "Mother".

34:52.120 --> 34:53.239
So tiny.

34:54.440 --> 34:56.480
His voice melted my heart.

34:57.520 --> 34:58.640
And someone

34:59.960 --> 35:02.000
was getting flustered with jealousy.

35:02.720 --> 35:03.880
Do you remember?

35:03.960 --> 35:05.960
He had a high fever
in the middle of the night.

35:06.680 --> 35:08.040
I said he'd be fine,

35:08.800 --> 35:10.120
but you insisted on taking him out

35:10.200 --> 35:12.080
to find a physician.

35:12.160 --> 35:15.240
You even gathered
every physician in the village.

35:16.160 --> 35:18.080
Someone was even jealous of himself.

35:22.880 --> 35:24.120
Even knowing it was an illusion,

35:25.040 --> 35:26.400
after so long,

35:27.240 --> 35:28.680
I still got drawn into it.

35:31.120 --> 35:32.400
You don't want to stay here.

35:33.600 --> 35:35.120
For me,

35:35.200 --> 35:37.920
I get to see my late brother every day.

35:39.400 --> 35:40.400
But you're different.

35:43.960 --> 35:45.080
You're trapped

35:45.920 --> 35:48.480
in an illusory life
that has nothing to do with you.

35:53.720 --> 35:55.240
You've worn it for years.

35:56.760 --> 35:58.120
<i>I was thinking…</i>

35:59.160 --> 36:01.560
-Are you all right?
-<i>Before my eyesight gets worse,</i>

36:01.640 --> 36:03.560
<i>I'd make you a new one.</i>

36:03.640 --> 36:04.760
<i>It's fine.</i>

36:04.840 --> 36:06.320
I like this one.

36:07.560 --> 36:09.720
This bracelet means forever.

36:10.800 --> 36:12.240
If it breaks, it's a bad omen.

36:14.000 --> 36:15.400
It should be kept safe,

36:16.240 --> 36:19.000
not worn every day as I do.

36:20.920 --> 36:21.760
So,

36:24.960 --> 36:26.120
you knew it all along.

36:31.880 --> 36:33.080
Instead of putting it away,

36:34.400 --> 36:35.240
I'd rather wear it.

36:36.760 --> 36:37.760
Every time I see it,

36:39.040 --> 36:40.560
I can't help but wonder.

36:42.920 --> 36:44.680
Have you started to like this place?

36:47.240 --> 36:48.360
We've both changed.

36:49.680 --> 36:50.800
And yet,

36:51.480 --> 36:53.600
it feels like this is who
we were meant to be.

36:59.480 --> 37:01.200
That's why I hoped it would break.

37:03.160 --> 37:04.560
Because no matter how much we like it,

37:05.520 --> 37:08.040
this life doesn't belong to us.

37:09.360 --> 37:11.120
Like something stolen,

37:12.240 --> 37:13.360
even if you love it,

37:15.560 --> 37:17.560
it never sits right in your heart.

37:18.720 --> 37:20.760
Then why make me a new one?

37:21.640 --> 37:23.000
Over and over again.

37:23.520 --> 37:24.600
Isn't that tiring?

37:25.960 --> 37:27.880
When you crouch too long in the dark,

37:27.960 --> 37:29.560
you start to crave warmth.

37:30.520 --> 37:33.680
And once you crave it,
you do foolish things.

37:36.440 --> 37:37.880
There are many people

37:38.720 --> 37:40.200
who are full of contradictions.

37:41.200 --> 37:44.280
Maybe that's why even the smartest

37:44.360 --> 37:47.000
can do the most foolish things.

37:47.600 --> 37:48.640
Love

37:48.720 --> 37:51.560
can make someone put down their blade.

37:51.640 --> 37:54.400
Make the proud bow their head.

37:55.200 --> 37:58.680
Make the sharpest mind
to do the most foolish things.

38:06.040 --> 38:06.880
And you?

38:08.160 --> 38:10.520
<i>Staying here with me</i>
<i>and doing all these foolish things,</i>

38:11.040 --> 38:12.240
<i>aren't you tired?</i>

38:24.880 --> 38:25.840
<i>Me?</i>

38:27.600 --> 38:29.240
Maybe I'm just selfish.

38:30.760 --> 38:32.080
I'd rather we suffer together

38:32.680 --> 38:34.520
than be left alone.

38:42.360 --> 38:43.920
You're the fool.

38:52.880 --> 38:53.800
All of this

38:54.760 --> 38:56.720
will end someday.

38:57.320 --> 38:58.160
Yes.

38:59.200 --> 39:00.680
Once we learn the truth,

39:01.480 --> 39:02.320
we'll leave.

39:04.000 --> 39:05.040
When that time comes,

39:07.320 --> 39:08.440
could you

39:09.720 --> 39:11.160
make me another bracelet?

39:12.400 --> 39:13.440
One that's stronger.

39:14.920 --> 39:16.480
One I can wear for a lifetime.

39:28.880 --> 39:29.720
Sure.

41:27.760 --> 41:28.920
Stop it.

41:42.320 --> 41:43.480
What are you doing?

41:46.240 --> 41:47.200
What about you?

41:50.560 --> 41:51.560
What are you doing here?

41:51.640 --> 41:53.000
Will severing your own tail really help?

41:53.720 --> 41:56.160
Xiaowei was always on the run,
hunted by the Never-Ending Curse.

41:56.880 --> 41:58.400
And you'll lose all your senses.

42:00.520 --> 42:02.240
Going blind again doesn't scare me.

42:03.800 --> 42:05.200
I'm used to it.

42:07.720 --> 42:08.800
All these years,

42:11.200 --> 42:12.800
you've been by my side.

42:16.720 --> 42:17.720
I've grown used to that too.

42:23.280 --> 42:24.720
Let me face this with you.

42:26.360 --> 42:28.000
I have to face it alone.

42:30.320 --> 42:32.120
Tonight is the full moon.

42:33.240 --> 42:34.840
Everyone from the Formless Moon Sect,

42:36.520 --> 42:37.680
including Jiu Ying,

42:39.760 --> 42:41.920
will find out the secret
between Chi Wen and me.

42:42.800 --> 42:44.240
Other than severing my tail,

42:44.320 --> 42:45.760
I have no choice.

42:46.720 --> 42:47.880
All I can do is admit defeat.

42:49.600 --> 42:50.720
Wangyan,

42:50.800 --> 42:52.480
this was all Jiu Ying's scheme.

42:53.320 --> 42:54.640
Don't be afraid.

42:54.720 --> 42:55.760
Don't hide.

42:56.760 --> 42:57.680
I'm here.

42:58.960 --> 43:00.000
I'll always stay with you.

43:03.720 --> 43:04.880
All right?

43:08.200 --> 43:09.600
It's too late.

43:13.360 --> 43:14.200
Too late.

43:15.120 --> 43:16.960
-Tonight…
-I know.

43:17.880 --> 43:18.960
I know everything.

43:19.760 --> 43:21.560
Tonight is the full moon.

43:21.640 --> 43:23.800
I can't stop them from summoning you back.

43:26.600 --> 43:27.760
But believe me.

43:30.280 --> 43:31.600
I will come find you.

43:33.240 --> 43:34.160
Wait for me.

43:35.280 --> 43:36.960
I'll bring you back, no matter what.
